Easy Sio Bak aka Roast Pork Belly anyone? ⁣
⁣
⁣
Easy Airfryer Recipe⬇️⁣
Ingredients:⁣
Fresh pork belly⁣
Five spice powder⁣
Pink salt⁣
⁣
⁣
Instructions:⁣
1. Rinse and dab dry pork belly. ⁣
2. Marinate pork belly with five spice powder and pink salt. ⁣
3. Airfry at 200 degree for 30 mins with skin up. ⁣
🔺 Best to marinate the meat, skip the skin and leave it uncover in the fridge overnight to let it dry and for crackling skin. (For this I didn't bcoz I saw @onlychildsyndrome.gg 's post so this is impromptu 😂) ⁣
